@page "/listgroup"

<PageTitle>列表组 (List Group) - Bootstrap 展示</PageTitle>

<h2>📃 列表组 (List Group)</h2>
<p class="lead">灵活的列表组件：基础、链接式、无边框、编号、复选框及情景变体。</p>

<h5 class="mt-4">基础列表组 (Basic List Group)</h5>
<div class="border rounded p-4 bg-light mb-4">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <ul class="list-group mb-3">
                <li class="list-group-item">列表项</li>
                <li class="list-group-item">第二项</li>
                <li class="list-group-item">第三项</li>
                <li class="list-group-item">第四项</li>
                <li class="list-group-item disabled">禁用项</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <ul class="list-group">
                <li class="list-group-item active">活跃项（高亮）</li>
                <li class="list-group-item">普通项</li>
                <li class="list-group-item list-group-item-action">可操作项（悬停效果）</li>
                <li class="list-group-item d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
                    带徽章的项
                    <span class="badge bg-primary rounded-pill">14</span>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<h5>链接式列表组 (Link-based List Group)</h5>
<div class="border rounded p-4 bg-light mb-4">
    <div class="list-group">
        <a href="#" class="list-group-item list-group-item-action active">活跃链接项</a>
        <a href="#" class="list-group-item list-group-item-action">第二个链接项</a>
        <a href="#" class="list-group-item list-group-item-action">第三个链接项</a>
        <a href="#" class="list-group-item list-group-item-action disabled">禁用链接</a>
    </div>
</div>

<h5>无边框与编号 (Flush & Numbered)</h5>
<div class="border rounded p-4 bg-light mb-4">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <p class="fw-bold">无边框（无外部边框）</p>
            <ul class="list-group list-group-flush border rounded mb-3">
                <li class="list-group-item">无边框项 1</li>
                <li class="list-group-item">无边框项 2</li>
                <li class="list-group-item">无边框项 3</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <p class="fw-bold">编号列表</p>
            <ol class="list-group list-group-numbered mb-3">
                <li class="list-group-item">编号项一</li>
                <li class="list-group-item">编号项二</li>
                <li class="list-group-item">编号项三</li>
            </ol>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<h5>情景变体 (Contextual Variants)</h5>
<div class="border rounded p-4 bg-light mb-4">
    <ul class="list-group">
        @foreach (var c in new[]{"","primary","secondary","success","danger","warning","info","light","dark"})
        {
            <li class="list-group-item list-group-item-@c">
                @(string.IsNullOrEmpty(c) ? "默认 (Default)" : c) 列表组项
            </li>
        }
    </ul>
</div>

<h5>带复选框与单选框 (With Checkboxes & Radios)</h5>
<div class="border rounded p-4 bg-light mb-4">
    <div class="list-group">
        <label class="list-group-item">
            <input class="form-check-input me-1" type="checkbox" value=""> 第一个复选框
        </label>
        <label class="list-group-item">
            <input class="form-check-input me-1" type="checkbox" value="" checked> 第二个复选框（已勾选）
        </label>
        <label class="list-group-item">
            <input class="form-check-input me-1" type="checkbox" value=""> 第三个复选框
        </label>
    </div>
    <hr>
    <div class="list-group">
        <label class="list-group-item">
            <input class="form-check-input me-1" type="radio" name="listGroupRadio" value="" checked> 单选项 1
        </label>
        <label class="list-group-item">
            <input class="form-check-input me-1" type="radio" name="listGroupRadio" value=""> 单选项 2
        </label>
        <label class="list-group-item">
            <input class="form-check-input me-1" type="radio" name="listGroupRadio" value=""> 单选项 3
        </label>
    </div>
</div>

<h5>自定义内容 (Custom Content)</h5>
<div class="border rounded p-4 bg-light mb-4">
    <div class="list-group">
        <a href="#" class="list-group-item list-group-item-action">
            <div class="d-flex w-100 justify-content-between">
                <h5 class="mb-1">列表组标题</h5>
                <small>3 天前</small>
            </div>
            <p class="mb-1">一些占位文本，以及第二行内容。</p>
            <small class="text-muted">还有一些柔和的脚注文本。</small>
        </a>
        <a href="#" class="list-group-item list-group-item-action">
            <div class="d-flex w-100 justify-content-between">
                <h5 class="mb-1">另一个标题</h5>
                <small class="text-muted">1 天前</small>
            </div>
            <p class="mb-1">第二项的另一种内容。</p>
            <small class="text-muted">Donec id elit non mi porta.</small>
        </a>
    </div>
</div>
